review_blob: Soft bite initially but smooth after taste in this full bodied stout.  Pours nicely in to class from the bottle with minimal head.  Aroma is pleasant as well.
beer_name: Big Sky Slow Elk Oatmeal Stout

review_blob: Classic Scotch ale color and texture.  A little weak on flavor but satisfying out of the 22oz bottle.
Smooth easy to drink with rich Carmel color.  Favorite of mine on a hot summer day or cold winter one too.
beer_name: Kettle House Cold Smoke Scotch Ale
